<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
	<% include partials/head %>
</head>

<body class="container">
	<% include partials/navbar %>
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-sm-4">
		</br>
			<div class="text-center" id="desktop-icon"><i class="fa fa-desktop" style="font-size:72px;color:blue"></i></div>
			</br>
			<table class="table text-left">	
				<tr><td><strong>Desktop ID</td></strong><td id="instanceId"><%= user.instanceId %></td></tr>
				<tr><td><strong>Desktop IP</td></strong><td id="<%= user.ipAllocationId %>"><%= user.instanceIP %></td></tr>
				<tr><td><strong>Status</td></strong><td id="instanceStatus"><%= user.instanceStatus %></td></tr>
			</table>
			<div class="alert alert-danger" id="error"></div>
			<div class="text-center"><img src="/images/loader.gif" id="loader" style="display:none" /></div>
		</div>
		<div class="col-sm-4">
		<div class="spacer"></div>
			<button id="create-btn" data-url="/users/<%= user.username %>/createInstance" type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">Launch Windows PC</button></br>
			<!-- <button id="start-btn" data-url="/users/<%= user.username %>/<%= user.instanceId %>/startInstance" type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">Start</button></br> -->
			<button id='shutdown-btn' data-url="/users/<%= user.username %>/<%= user.instanceId %>/stopInstance" type="submit" class="btn btn-danger btn-block">Shutdown</button></br>
			<button id="delete-btn" data-url="/users/<%= user.username %>/deleteInstance" type="submit" class="btn btn-danger btn-block">Delete</button></br>
		</div>
		<div class="col-sm-4">
			<div class="text-left well">
				<h3>Instructions <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-bullhorn"></span></h3>    
				<p></p>
				<dl>
					<dt>Launch Windows PC</dt>
					<dd>Starts a Windows 10 PC or creates a new one</dd>
					<dt>Shutdown</dt>
					<dd>Stops the running PC.</br><small>NOTE: Shutdown from Windows will not stop the PC. Make sure to shutdown from here.</small></dd>
					<dt>Delete</dt>
					<dd>Permanently deletes the PC.</br><small>NOTE: All data on the PC will be lost.</small></dd></br>
					<div>
						<dt>Connecting to the system</dt>
						<dd>On Windows, search for Remote Desktop Connection on the Start Menu. Enter the Desktop IP, username (as <mark>'MHSVDI\username'</mark>) and password. Save & Connect</dd></br>
						<dd>On Mac, install Microsoft Remote Desktop 10. Add a new connection with the Desktop IP, username (as <mark>'MHSVDI\username'</mark>) and password. Save & Connect</dd>
						<dd class="bg-danger"><small>NOTE: A new PC takes about 3 to 5 mins to register with the domain.</small></dd>
					</div>
				</dl>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<p hidden id="username" data-username="<%= user.username %>"></p>
	<% include partials/script %>
</body>
</html>